        <h2 id="main-framework-and-checklist" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950">Main framework and checklist</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700">To approach lead generation systems effectively, owners should follow a clear framework and checklist. Here are the key decision criteria, quality signals, and next actions to consider:</p>
        <p class="text-slate-700">**Decision Criteria:** Evaluate the lead generation system&#39;s ability to capture, nurture, and convert leads efficiently. Consider the system&#39;s scalability, flexibility, and integration with other tools.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-700">**Quality Signals:** Look for consistent lead engagement, high conversion rates, and positive customer feedback. Regularly review and analyze these metrics to ensure the system&#39;s performance.</p>
        <p class="text-slate-700">**Next Action:** Based on your evaluation, identify areas for improvement and prioritize changes. Regularly review and update the system to maintain its effectiveness.</p>
      </section>
